(660, 'Monetarists want to[][]', 'use government spending and job programs during economic downturns to inject money into the economy.[]', 'reduce taxes in order to stimulate the growth of the money supply.[]', 'hold the growth in money supply to equal the rise in the gross national product after inflation.[]', 'keep the government\'s hands off the economy. []', 3, 3, 'hard'),
