(967, 'Prior to the Supreme Court\'s rulings in the 1960s to end the malapportionment, ________ areaswere overrepresented in many state legislatures.[][]', 'urban[]', 'suburban[]', 'rural[]', 'none of the above []', 3, 1, 'hard'),
