(331, 'If the United States had a multiparty system,[][]', 'third parties would come to dominate politics.[]', 'the necessity for coalitions would be eliminated.[]', 'each party would have more distinct policy positions.[]', 'each party would move to the ideological center. []', 3, 3, 'medium'),
